66
00:06:38,788 --> 00:06:39,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun...</font>

67
00:06:43,188 --> 00:06:44,858
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengetahui aku Seja.</font>

68
00:06:46,158 --> 00:06:48,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mengetahuinya.</font>

69
