<font color=#FFFF00>Sun-ah.</font>

75
00:07:44,128 --> 00:07:45,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi.</font>

76
00:07:47,088 --> 00:07:48,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau ingat?</font>

77
00:07:48,958 --> 00:07:50,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Guru pernah berkata...</font>

78
00:07:51,988 --> 00:07:54,088
<font color=#FFFF00>..takdir itu bagaikan sungai.</font>

79
00:07:54,528 --> 00:07:56,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat sungai marah...</font>

80
00:07:57,488 --> 00:07:59,628
<font color=#FFFF00>...segala sesuatu ditelan olehnya.</font>

81
00:08:00,628 --> 00:08:02,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Semuanya lenyap...</font>

