87
00:08:27,628 --> 00:08:29,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Tenanglah.</font>

88
00:08:31,728 --> 00:08:35,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Untuk menghentikan takdir membuat Aghassi sengsara,</font>

89
