109
00:10:10,828 --> 00:10:14,328
<font color=#FFFF00>...maupun orang itu mencintai Aghassi.</font>

110
00:10:14,328 --> 00:10:15,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Menarik sekali.</font>

111
00:10:16,988 --> 00:10:21,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Si asli dan palsu mencintai wanita yang sama.</font>

112
00:10:23,098 --> 00:10:24,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu...</font>

113
00:10:24,988 --> 00:10:28,488
<font color=#FFFF00>...bisa menangkap dua kelinci dengan satu perangkap.</font>

114
00:10:32,628 --> 00:10:34,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya membawa kembali sisa penawarnya.</font>

115
00:10:38,528 --> 00:10:39,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Penawar ini...</font>

116
