117
00:10:45,558 --> 00:10:49,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun menjadi racun terhadap yang tidak ketergantungan.</font>

118
00:10:52,058 --> 00:10:54,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengiriminya penawar asli,</font>

119
00:10:55,058 --> 00:10:57,328
