121
00:11:04,058 --> 00:11:05,558
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik, Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

122
00:11:10,688 --> 00:11:14,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha, apa yang Dae Mok katakan?</font>

123
00:11:15,188 --> 00:11:17,058
