00:16:07,558 --> 00:16:09,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Gerbang Geonchunmun, Gerbang Yeongchumun,</font>

191
00:16:09,328 --> 00:16:11,488
<font color=#FFFF00>dan Gerbang Gwanghwamun Gate sudah dijaga ketat.</font>

192
00:16:11,488 --> 00:16:13,828
