193
00:16:14,828 --> 00:16:18,158
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus lekas pergi sebelum Dae Mok menangkapmu.</font>

194
00:16:21,758 --> 00:16:24,058
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah kebaikan terakhirku...</font>

195
00:16:25,858 --> 00:16:27,128
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang...</font>

196
00:16:29,188 --> 00:16:31,458
<font color=#FFFF00>...dapat kuberikan.</font>

197
00:16:40,558 --> 00:16:42,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila kau bisa keluar hidup-hidup,</font>

198
00:16:43,758 --> 00:16:47,158
<font color=#FFFF00>jangan pernah kembali...</font>

199
00:16:48,358 --> 00:16:49,558
<font color=#FFFF00>...kemari.</font>

200
00:16:51,188 --> 00:16:54,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau kembali, maka...</font>

201
00:16:54,928 --> 00:16:57,858
