202
00:17:12,958 --> 00:17:14,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

203
00:17:14,258 --> 00:17:17,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada pasukan dimana-mana, jadi hamba menyusul karena kuatir.</font>

204
00:17:17,458 --> 00:17:18,658
