205
00:17:19,588 --> 00:17:20,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Lewat sana!</font>

206
00:17:22,158 --> 00:17:23,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Guru.</font>

207
00:17:32,558 --> 00:17:36,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok tahu aku masih hidup.</font>

208
00:17:37,258 --> 00:17:40,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus lekas keluar lewat Gerbang Shinmumun.</font>

209
00:17:52,658 --> 00:17:54,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka pengkhianat! Tangkap mereka!</font>

210
