211
00:18:06,128 --> 00:18:09,058
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka lewat sana! Tangkap mereka!</font>

212
00:18:11,928 --> 00:18:13,158
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti!</font>

213
00:18:13,158 --> 00:18:14,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Tangkap mereka!</font>

214
00:18:17,298 --> 00:18:19,058
<font color=#FFFF00>- Temukan mereka!
- Tangkap!</font>

215
00:18:19,058 --> 00:18:21,588
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mereka lewat sana!
- Tangkap!</font>

216
00:18:21,588 --> 00:18:22,758
<font color=#FFFF00>Lewat sini!</font>

217
00:19:14,828 --> 00:19:16,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa kau kemari?</font>

218
00:19:16,228 --> 00:19:19,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala Kasim.
Apakah melihat ada orang mencurigakan?</font>

219
00:19:21,128 --> 00:19:24,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kalian melihat orang mencurigakan?</font>

220
00:19:24,128 --> 00:19:25,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya tidak lihat.</font>

221
00:19:25,488 --> 00:19:29,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya melihat ada dua pria aneh memanjat dinding.</font>

222
00:19:47,188 --> 00:19:49,058
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mirip dengan dia.</font>

223
00:19:50,658 --> 00:19:52,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sangat mirip....</font>

224
00:19:52,858 --> 00:19:55,928
<font color=#FFFF00>...dengan pencuri takhta Raja,</font>

225
00:19:55,928 --> 00:19:57,488
<font color=#FFFF00>si pengkhianat.</font>

226
00:19:58,758 --> 00:20:02,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu.... apa maksudnya?</font>

227
00:20:26,758 --> 00:20:29,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kehilangan Seja?</font>

228
00:20:29,458 --> 00:20:31,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya pantas mati, Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

229
00:20:31,558 --> 00:20:33,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Aneh sekali.</font>

230
00:20:33,088 --> 00:20:35,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebuah perangkap sempurna begitu...</font>

231
00:20:35,458 --> 00:20:37,488
<font color=#FFFF00>...seharusnya tidak akan gagal.</font>

232
00:20:40,258 --> 00:20:42,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah ada yang tidak kuketahui...</font>

233
00:20:42,588 --> 00:20:44,958
<font color=#FFFF00>...tentang orang dalam istana?</font>

234
00:20:48,958 --> 00:20:50,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya bisa...</font>

235
00:20:51,558 --> 00:20:53,658
<font color=#FFFF00>...menatapnya saat tidur.</font>

236
00:20:53,828 --> 00:20:55,558
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan hamba, Cheonha.</font>

237
00:20:55,758 --> 00:20:57,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena tidak berhenti menangis,</font>

238
00:20:58,758 --> 00:21:00,758
<font color=#FFFF00>dia pun kurang istirahat.</font>

239
00:21:01,488 --> 00:21:04,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Hamba memberinya obat tidur agar dapat istirahat.</font>

240
00:21:05,028 --> 00:21:07,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah itu mempunyai efek samping?</font>

241
00:21:07,858 --> 00:21:09,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Mohon jangan cemas.</font>

242
00:21:10,058 --> 00:21:13,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Obatnya dosis kecil, hanya agar dia tertidur.</font>

243
00:21:25,388 --> 00:21:27,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Jaga dia dengan baik.</font>

244
00:21:29,058 --> 00:21:30,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Gadis ini...</font>

245
00:21:33,928 --> 00:21:36,658
<font color=#FFFF00>...paling berarti bagiku di dunia.</font>

246
00:21:39,958 --> 00:21:42,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik, Cheonha.</font>

247
00:21:50,558 --> 00:21:52,058
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan aku!</font>

248
00:21:52,658 --> 00:21:54,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau sungguh Seja Jeoha,</font>

249
00:21:54,488 --> 00:21:57,158
<font color=#FFFF00>kenapa selama ini kau berpura-pura sebagai Chun Soo...</font>

250
00:21:57,158 --> 00:21:58,688
<font color=#FFFF00>....Doryongnim?</font>

251
00:21:59,158 --> 00:22:00,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau menipuku?</font>

252
00:22:01,858 --> 00:22:05,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Enyah! Aku tidak mau lagi bertemu denganmu.</font>

253
00:22:05,358 --> 00:22:06,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Lekas enyah!</font>

254
00:22:09,658 --> 00:22:11,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila kau bisa keluar hidup-hidup,</font>

255
00:22:11,828 --> 00:22:16,658
<font color=#FFFF00>jangan pernah kembali kemari.</font>

256
00:22:20,058 --> 00:22:22,758
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau kembali, maka...</font>

257
00:22:23,558 --> 00:22:26,558
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku akan membunuhmu dengan tanganku sendiri.</font>

258
00:22:49,558 --> 00:22:51,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun Aghassi.</font>

259
00:22:51,558 --> 00:22:53,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus bangun sekarang.</font>

260
00:22:55,058 --> 00:22:57,558
<font color=#FFFF00>Jusang Cheonha akan segera kemari.</font>

261
00:23:01,688 --> 00:23:05,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, kau kan yang di Biro Perdagangan itu.</font>

262
00:23:07,858 --> 00:23:09,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Mohon ampuni aku.</font>

263
00:23:11,088 --> 00:23:13,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah kuduga, kau pasti bersamanya.</font>

264
00:23:14,158 --> 00:23:15,558
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa dia ke luar.</font>

265
00:23:15,558 --> 00:23:16,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

266
00:23:27,858 --> 00:23:31,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun Aghassi diculik oleh Dae Mok.</font>

267
00:23:32,558 --> 00:23:33,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

268
00:23:33,958 --> 00:23:36,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa Dae Mok menculik Ga Eun?</font>

269
00:23:36,858 --> 00:23:38,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mengirim pesan untuk Seja Jeoha.</font>

270
00:23:39,088 --> 00:23:41,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang membawa Ga Eun Aghassi
dan bila ingin kembali,</font>

271
00:23:42,228 --> 00:23:44,058
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda harus menemui Dae Mok sendirian.</font>

272
00:23:46,658 --> 00:23:48,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku adalah Seja...</font>

273
00:23:50,058 --> 00:23:52,058
<font color=#FFFF00>...bagaimana kau bisa tahu?</font>

274
00:23:55,828 --> 00:23:58,558
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya sudah tahu\ bahkan sejak di Biro Perdagangan.</font>

275
00:23:59,258 --> 00:24:02,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun yang terpenting sekarang adalah Dae Mok juga tahu...</font>

276
00:24:03,388 --> 00:24:04,958
<font color=#FFFF00>...Doryongnim adalah Seja Jeoha...</font>

277
00:24:04,958 --> 00:24:07,558
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menjadikan Ga Eun Aghassi sebagai sandera.</font>

278
00:24:10,328 --> 00:24:11,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang akan Anda lakukan?</font>

279
00:24:11,658 --> 00:24:14,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa lagi? Aku akan pergi sekarang dan menyelamatkan Ga Eun--</font>

280
00:24:14,858 --> 00:24:16,058
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh...</font>

281
00:24:17,128 --> 00:24:19,058
<font color=#FFFF00>...Anda akan menyelamatkan dia?</font>

282
00:24:20,858 --> 00:24:23,158
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu itu?</font>

283
00:24:25,458 --> 00:24:26,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Anda pergi sekarang,</font>

284
00:24:27,858 --> 00:24:30,658
